00:02:25.264 --> 00:02:32.480
subtract 6x from both sides of the equation to get 2x plus 4 equals 18. Next,

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:39.210
we'll subtract 4 from both sides to isolate the 2x. So, 2x will equal 14.

00:02:39.210 --> 00:02:44.350
